@startuml
title Sơ đồ tuần tự - Chức năng đổi email

actor "Người dùng" as User
boundary "_ChangeEmailScreenState" as ChangeEmailScreenState
boundary "_VerifyOtpScreenState" as VerifyOtpScreenState
control "TokenStorageService" as TokenStorageService
control "AuthApiService" as AuthApiService
control "ClientController" as ClientController
control "ClientServiceImpl" as ClientServiceImpl
database "ClientRepository" as ClientRepository
control "OtpCodeUtil" as OtpCodeUtil
database "RedisTemplate" as RedisTemplate
control "EmailUtil" as EmailUtil
control "JavaMailSender" as JavaMailSender
control "JwtUtil" as JwtUtil
control "ClientMapper" as ClientMapper
control "Navigator" as Navigator

User -> ChangeEmailScreenState: 1: nhập email mới và bấm Xác thực email
activate ChangeEmailScreenState

ChangeEmailScreenState -> ChangeEmailScreenState: 2: _verifyEmail()
activate ChangeEmailScreenState

ChangeEmailScreenState -> TokenStorageService: 3: gọi
activate TokenStorageService
TokenStorageService -> TokenStorageService: 4: getToken()
activate TokenStorageService
deactivate TokenStorageService
TokenStorageService --> ChangeEmailScreenState: 5: trả về kết quả
deactivate TokenStorageService

ChangeEmailScreenState -> AuthApiService: 6: gọi
activate AuthApiService
AuthApiService -> AuthApiService: 7: preChangeEmail(token, newEmail)
activate AuthApiService

AuthApiService -> ClientController: 8: gọi API POST /client/email/pre-change
activate ClientController
ClientController -> ClientController: 9: changePassword(PreChangeEmailRequest)
activate ClientController

ClientController -> ClientServiceImpl: 10: gọi
activate ClientServiceImpl
ClientServiceImpl -> ClientServiceImpl: 11: preChangEmailRequest(newEmail)
activate ClientServiceImpl

ClientServiceImpl -> ClientRepository: 12: gọi
activate ClientRepository
ClientRepository -> ClientRepository: 13: existsByEmailAndActive(newEmail, true)
activate ClientRepository
deactivate ClientRepository
ClientRepository --> ClientServiceImpl: 14: trả về kết quả
deactivate ClientRepository

ClientServiceImpl -> OtpCodeUtil: 15: gọi
activate OtpCodeUtil
OtpCodeUtil -> OtpCodeUtil: 16: generateOtpCode()
activate OtpCodeUtil
deactivate OtpCodeUtil
OtpCodeUtil --> ClientServiceImpl: 17: trả về kết quả
deactivate OtpCodeUtil

ClientServiceImpl -> RedisTemplate: 18: gọi
activate RedisTemplate
RedisTemplate -> RedisTemplate: 19: opsForValue().set(newEmail, code, 5, TimeUnit.MINUTES)
activate RedisTemplate
deactivate RedisTemplate
RedisTemplate --> ClientServiceImpl: 20: trả về kết quả
deactivate RedisTemplate

ClientServiceImpl -> EmailUtil: 21: gọi
activate EmailUtil
EmailUtil -> EmailUtil: 22: sendOtpEmail(newEmail, code, title, message, 5)
activate EmailUtil

EmailUtil -> JavaMailSender: 23: gọi
activate JavaMailSender
JavaMailSender -> JavaMailSender: 24: send(mimeMessage)
activate JavaMailSender
deactivate JavaMailSender
JavaMailSender --> EmailUtil: 25: trả về kết quả
deactivate JavaMailSender

deactivate EmailUtil
EmailUtil --> ClientServiceImpl: 26: trả về kết quả
deactivate EmailUtil

deactivate ClientServiceImpl
ClientServiceImpl --> ClientController: 27: trả về kết quả
deactivate ClientServiceImpl

deactivate ClientController
ClientController --> AuthApiService: 28: trả về kết quả
deactivate ClientController

deactivate AuthApiService
AuthApiService --> ChangeEmailScreenState: 29: trả về kết quả
deactivate AuthApiService

ChangeEmailScreenState -> Navigator: 30: gọi
activate Navigator
Navigator -> Navigator: 31: pushReplacementNamed(AppRoutes.verifyOtp, VerifyOtpArgs)
activate Navigator
deactivate Navigator
Navigator --> ChangeEmailScreenState: 32: trả về kết quả
deactivate Navigator

deactivate ChangeEmailScreenState

ChangeEmailScreenState --> User: 33: điều hướng đến màn hình nhập OTP
deactivate ChangeEmailScreenState

User -> VerifyOtpScreenState: 34: nhập OTP và bấm Xác thực
activate VerifyOtpScreenState

VerifyOtpScreenState -> VerifyOtpScreenState: 35: _submitOtp(VerifyOtpArgs)
activate VerifyOtpScreenState

VerifyOtpScreenState -> TokenStorageService: 36: gọi
activate TokenStorageService
TokenStorageService -> TokenStorageService: 37: getToken()
activate TokenStorageService
deactivate TokenStorageService
TokenStorageService --> VerifyOtpScreenState: 38: trả về kết quả
deactivate TokenStorageService

VerifyOtpScreenState -> AuthApiService: 39: gọi
activate AuthApiService
AuthApiService -> AuthApiService: 40: changeEmail(token, otp, newEmail)
activate AuthApiService

AuthApiService -> ClientController: 41: gọi API PUT /client/email/change
activate ClientController
ClientController -> ClientController: 42: changeEmail(ChangeEmailRequest, token)
activate ClientController

ClientController -> ClientServiceImpl: 43: gọi
activate ClientServiceImpl
ClientServiceImpl -> ClientServiceImpl: 44: changeEmail(ChangeEmailRequest, token)
activate ClientServiceImpl

ClientServiceImpl -> JwtUtil: 45: gọi
activate JwtUtil
JwtUtil -> JwtUtil: 46: getClaims(token)
activate JwtUtil
deactivate JwtUtil
JwtUtil --> ClientServiceImpl: 47: trả về kết quả
deactivate JwtUtil

ClientServiceImpl -> ClientRepository: 48: gọi
activate ClientRepository
ClientRepository -> ClientRepository: 49: findByEmailAndActive(oldEmail, true)
activate ClientRepository
deactivate ClientRepository
ClientRepository --> ClientServiceImpl: 50: trả về kết quả
deactivate ClientRepository

ClientServiceImpl -> RedisTemplate: 51: gọi
activate RedisTemplate
RedisTemplate -> RedisTemplate: 52: opsForValue().get(newEmail)
activate RedisTemplate
deactivate RedisTemplate
RedisTemplate --> ClientServiceImpl: 53: trả về kết quả
deactivate RedisTemplate

ClientServiceImpl -> ClientRepository: 54: gọi
activate ClientRepository
ClientRepository -> ClientRepository: 55: save(Client)
activate ClientRepository
deactivate ClientRepository
ClientRepository --> ClientServiceImpl: 56: trả về kết quả
deactivate ClientRepository

ClientServiceImpl -> RedisTemplate: 57: gọi
activate RedisTemplate
RedisTemplate -> RedisTemplate: 58: delete(newEmail)
activate RedisTemplate
deactivate RedisTemplate
RedisTemplate --> ClientServiceImpl: 59: trả về kết quả
deactivate RedisTemplate

ClientServiceImpl -> RedisTemplate: 60: gọi
activate RedisTemplate
RedisTemplate -> RedisTemplate: 61: opsForValue().set(claims.id, token, ttl)
activate RedisTemplate
deactivate RedisTemplate
RedisTemplate --> ClientServiceImpl: 62: trả về kết quả
deactivate RedisTemplate

ClientServiceImpl -> JwtUtil: 63: gọi
activate JwtUtil
JwtUtil -> JwtUtil: 64: generateToken(Client)
activate JwtUtil
deactivate JwtUtil
JwtUtil --> ClientServiceImpl: 65: trả về kết quả
deactivate JwtUtil

ClientServiceImpl -> ClientMapper: 66: gọi
activate ClientMapper
ClientMapper -> ClientMapper: 67: entityToResponse(Client)
activate ClientMapper
deactivate ClientMapper
ClientMapper --> ClientServiceImpl: 68: trả về kết quả
deactivate ClientMapper

deactivate ClientServiceImpl
ClientServiceImpl --> ClientController: 69: trả về kết quả
deactivate ClientServiceImpl

deactivate ClientController
ClientController --> AuthApiService: 70: trả về kết quả
deactivate ClientController

deactivate AuthApiService
AuthApiService --> VerifyOtpScreenState: 71: trả về kết quả
deactivate AuthApiService

VerifyOtpScreenState -> TokenStorageService: 72: gọi
activate TokenStorageService
TokenStorageService -> TokenStorageService: 73: saveAuthSession(newToken, userInfo)
activate TokenStorageService
deactivate TokenStorageService
TokenStorageService --> VerifyOtpScreenState: 74: trả về kết quả
deactivate TokenStorageService

VerifyOtpScreenState -> Navigator: 75: gọi
activate Navigator
Navigator -> Navigator: 76: popUntil(AppRoutes.profile)
activate Navigator
deactivate Navigator
Navigator --> VerifyOtpScreenState: 77: trả về kết quả
deactivate Navigator

deactivate VerifyOtpScreenState

VerifyOtpScreenState --> User: 78: điều hướng về màn hình hồ sơ
deactivate VerifyOtpScreenState

@enduml
